and that's why, actually,

00:01:57.283 --> 00:01:59.452 line:0%
there's been such an outpouring
of support around the country,

00:01:59.485 --> 00:02:02.421 line:0%
especially among women,
when this president

00:02:02.454 --> 00:02:05.658 line:0%
and this congress tried to,
you know, defund, as they said,

00:02:05.691 --> 00:02:08.594 line:0%
or prevent women from coming
to Planned Parenthood.

00:02:08.627 --> 00:02:10.796
We were able to beat back
the efforts

00:02:10.829 --> 00:02:12.899
to both defund
Planned Parenthood

00:02:12.932 --> 00:02:14.734
and repeal Obamacare.

00:02:14.767 --> 00:02:16.569
And Planned Parenthood's doors
are still open

00:02:16.602 --> 00:02:18.304
all across the United States
of America.

