had said she wanted to meet

00:02:32.952 --> 00:02:34.754 line:0%
to talk about
Planned Parenthood,

00:02:34.787 --> 00:02:37.790 line:0%
because her father had said he
was going to defund us again.

00:02:37.823 --> 00:02:40.126
And I thought, well,
if there's any chance

00:02:40.159 --> 00:02:43.162
to make my case, uh, I,
you know, wanted to do that.

00:02:43.195 --> 00:02:44.630
I did make my husband
come with me,

00:02:44.663 --> 00:02:46.666
so that I have a witness.

00:02:46.699 --> 00:02:50.036
But actually, really they,

00:02:50.069 --> 00:02:52.405
they didn't want to talk too
much about Planned Parenthood.

00:02:52.438 --> 00:02:54.407
Pretty much Jared Kushner said

00:02:54.440 --> 00:02:56.342
if we would quit
providing access

00:02:56.375 --> 00:02:59.045
to safe and legal abortion,
which we will not,

00:02:59.078 --> 00:03:02.181
then he would actually
get more federal funding

00:03:02.214 --> 00:03:04.150
for Planned Parenthood.
And I just said,

00:03:04.183 --> 00:03:05.952
"Look, we're not gonna trade off
women's rights

00:03:05.985 --> 00:03:07.820
in this country for money."

00:03:07.853 --> 00:03:09.755
That's just not who we are.

00:03:09.788 --> 00:03:11.724
(cheers and applause)

00:03:14.326 --> 00:03:16.295
That sounds like a deal.

00:03:16.328 --> 00:03:17.930
You got to give a little
to take a little.

00:03:17.963 --> 00:03:19.599
Well, we're not making deals

00:03:19.632 --> 00:03:21.334
about women's health
and women's rights.

00:03:21.367 --> 00:03:25.638
And actually,
Ivanka did say, she said,

00:03:25.671 --> 00:03:28.307 line:0%
"Well, you have to understand
my father's pro-life."

00:03:28.340 --> 00:03:30.109 line:0%
I said, "Well, he can have
his own opinion,

00:03:30.142 --> 00:03:31.811 line:0%
but he can't take away
the rights of millions

00:03:31.844 --> 00:03:33.412 line:0%
of American women that make
their own decisions

00:03:33.445 --> 00:03:35.114 line:0%
about their pregnancy.

