How can he say he's pro-life

00:03:42.087 --> 00:03:44.423
when he's trying
to deport dreamers,

00:03:44.456 --> 00:03:46.525
take away health care
from millions of people

00:03:46.558 --> 00:03:48.661
in this country
,and maternity benefits,

00:03:48.694 --> 00:03:50.763
all of the things that this
administration is trying to do?

00:03:50.796 --> 00:03:52.865
So I-I just feel
like he really needs

00:03:52.898 --> 00:03:54.667
to rethink what his values are.

00:03:54.700 --> 00:03:56.869
Well, he's very pro-his life.

00:03:56.902 --> 00:03:59.472
